#. Plugin Name of the plugin
#: post-types.php
msgid "Custom Post Types for Movies, Team Members and Supporters"
msgstr "Benutzerdefinierte Posttypen für Filme und mehr"

#. Plugin URI of the plugin
#: post-types.php
msgid "https://github.com/unikino-gegenlicht/custom-post-types"
msgstr "https://github.com/unikino-gegenlicht/custom-post-types"

#. Description of the plugin
#: post-types.php
msgid ""
"This plugin introduces custom post types to the WordPress installation which "
"enable handling of movies, team members and supporters"
msgstr ""
"Dieses Plugin erstellt neue Posttypen, mit denen Filme, Teammitglieder und "
"Untersützende verwaltet werden können"

